msgid ""
"   <p>We will enable again the automatic account configuration in Tails\n"
"   in the future. See [[!tails_ticket 6154]].</p>\n"
"   </div>\n"
msgstr ""
"   <p>Wir werden die automatische Konfiguration von Konten in Tails\n"
"   2.0 wieder aktivieren.</p>\n"
"   </div>\n"
